{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|p}} – a woodwind instrument. In the bronze inscriptions, {{zh-l|*亼}} (a flipped {{zh-l|*口}}) was added to show a mouth playing the instrument.

''{{w|Shuowen}}'' interprets it as an {{Han compound|品|侖|ls=ic|nocap=y}}.

{{zh-hanzi}}

# [[musical instrument]] which contains the bamboo tube and has three or other numbers of holes
# an ancient unit of volume
